name: Stop tying your hands... Better do it with me

metadata.name: Don't be afraid, look closer
metadata.description:
Shall we begin?)

Is your head filled with thoughts of work and ideas for projects? Are you thinking about how to become more productive and improve your quality of life? Or maybe you're thinking...?

No no, leave that for the real world, right now I want to spend time alone with you, not your busy mind)
 
This is 1 NFT in a collection of 9 photos each of which is unique and the only edition.  

Photo: ‪4 000 x 5 000‬ px.
